data.description: Endless and continuous upgrades! Surprising amount of privacy with the thoughtful positioning of improvements.  Over $100k in landscaping alone. Many owner requested upgrades when built including additional square footage, windows, expanded deck. Private fenced garden, backyard outside of fence built up for enough parking for two class A's.  Every bathroom filled with tile and granite. 10' Cei...ceilings and 8' interior doors on main level. Master plus 3 bedrooms feature en suites. Wolf range, 155 bottle wine cooler, separate built in drink fridge. Custom woodworking in office.  No boring "bonus" space; every area completed with high end finishes and design features. House sits closer to bluff than neighbors. Extra tall fence blocks neighbors below for unobstructed views to wildlife refuge, views of Knik inlet, Chugach and even Talkeetna Mountains. Zero stop lights to Anchorage. Bike paths in to Wasilla, trails through Hay Flats.  Better than new with alarm and cameras, window coverings, gutters, water softener, digital fridge stays. Lilacs, apple trees, rhubarb, raspberry and strawberries planted plus 70-80 shrubs. Ready for quick close!
